Initial setup after 'dd' of clean raspbian image

  login as pi
  sudo bash
  raspi-config
    1. expand filesystem
    2. change user pass for pi
    4. advanced
          set hostname (if desired)
          enable ssh
    5. internationalization
          locale
              pick en_US ISO-8859-1
                  select en_US
          timezone
              pick US/Pacific-New
          keyboard
              pick generic 104-key PC
              other
              english(US)
          wifi county
              US
  reboot
